sec.p:
Statistical analysis was performed with the R software version 4.1.2 (R Foundation for Statistical Computing, Vienna, Austria. URL: https://www.R-project.org/). The Pearson’s chi-squared test (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
